queries.sql: SELECT sum(saldomasuk) as sum FROM `transfer` WHERE month(tanggal) = month(CURRENT_DATE) AND YEAR(tanggal) = YEAR(CURRENT_DATE)

SELECT YEAR(tanggal) as tahun, MONTHNAME(tanggal) as bulan, sum(saldomasuk) as sum, `rekening` FROM `transfer` WHERE month(tanggal) = month(CURRENT_DATE) AND YEAR(tanggal) = 2025 GROUP BY `rekening`, `tahun`, `bulan` ORDER BY `tahun` DESC
SELECT YEAR(tanggal) AS tahun, MAX(tanggal) AS tanggal, SUM(saldomasuk) AS sum FROM `transfer` WHERE MONTH(tanggal) = '11' AND YEAR(tanggal) = '2025' GROUP BY `tahun` ORDER BY `tahun` DESC LIMIT 1
SELECT `program`, SUM(tunggakandu) as tungdu, SUM(tunggakantl) as tungtl, SUM(tunggakanspp) as tungspp FROM `santri` WHERE `program` = 'mandiri' GROUP BY `program`

SELECT `rekening`, `program`, SUM(daftarulang) AS daftarulang, SUM(tunggakan) AS tunggakan, SUM(spp) AS spp, SUM(uangsaku) AS saku, SUM(infaq) AS infaq, SUM(formulir) AS formulir FROM `detail` WHERE MONTH(tanggal) = '11' AND YEAR(tanggal) = '2025' GROUP BY `rekening`, `program` ORDER BY `rekening`

SELECT `rekening`, `program`, SUM(daftarulang) AS daftarulang, SUM(tunggakan) AS tunggakan, SUM(spp) AS spp, SUM(uangsaku) AS saku, SUM(infaq) AS infaq, SUM(formulir) AS formulir FROM `detail` WHERE MONTH(tanggal) = 10 AND YEAR(tanggal) = '2025' GROUP BY `rekening`, `program` ORDER BY `rekening`
